<section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-12 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
      왜 CarPlatform을 선택해야 할까요?
    </h2>
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center transform transition duration-300 hover:scale-105">
        <%= tabler_icon "discount-2", class: "w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400" %>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">실시간 최고 할인가</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">수많은 딜러사의 견적을 실시간으로 비교하여 가장 유리한 할인가를 찾아드립니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center transform transition duration-300 hover:scale-105">
        <%= tabler_icon "currency-dollar", class: "w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400" %>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">최저 금융상품 제안</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">개인 맞춤형 금융 상품을 비교 분석하여 가장 저렴한 이자율과 조건을 제공합니다.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 text-center transform transition duration-300 hover:scale-105">
        <%= tabler_icon "shield-check", class: "w-16 h-16 mx-auto mb-6 text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400" %>
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 text-gray-900 dark:text-white">투명하고 신뢰할 수 있는 정보</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">모든 차량 정보와 거래 과정은 투명하게 공개되어 안심하고 거래할 수 있습니다.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
